parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission hesitation and slipping can cause the vehicle to lurch or jerk, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Hesitation when accelerating
slipping or jerking between gears
delayed shifting
and lurching forward when merging into traffic or accelerating from a stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the upper right motor mount can cause vibration, noise, and loss of power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Vibrations between 45-60 mph
loss of power
and delayed acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electronic control system hesitation can cause the vehicle to hesitate or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle hesitation or stalling when shifting from second to third gear
delayed acceleration
and loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration of the vehicle can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly and uncontrollably
often when the driver is attempting to brake or slow down. The accelerator pedal may stick or become stuck
causing the vehicle to surge forward.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The accelerator pedal sticking can cause unintended acceleration, loss of control, and accidents.
symptoms: The accelerator pedal feels soft or spongy
sticks to the floor
or does not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The brakes do not engage or respond properly
causing the vehicle to continue moving even when the brake pedal is pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident, and may also lead to unexpected deployment of the airbag, causing accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag cover is separating from the dashboard
the airbag is protruding from the dashboard
the airbag is cracked or split
the airbag is not deploying in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident, and may also lead to unexpected deployment of the airbag, causing accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag is not deploying in the event of an accident
the airbag is deploying unexpectedly
the airbag system is not functioning properly.
